-- Jefferies banker Sage Kelly resigns - source
-- 
-- Wed Dec 17, 2014 11:23AM EST
-- None



Dec 17 (Reuters) - Sage Kelly, the head of Jefferies Group LLC's healthcare investment banking group, resigned, according to a person familiar with the matter.

Kelly, who is waging a bitter divorce battle with his estranged wife, had been on a leave of absence from the firm since November. [ID:nL1N0SP2I9]